Insider Activity


Individual




David H. Komansky



Mr. David H. Komansky is Co-Founder at Fieldpoint Private Bank & Trust, Inc., Independent Director at BlackRock, Inc., and President at Automated Security (Holdings) Plc. He is on the Board of Directors at BlackRock, Inc., NewYork-Presbyterian Hospital, The Norwalk Hospital Association, and Norwalk Health Services Corp.
Mr. Komansky was previously employed as Non-Executive Director by WPP Plc and Chairman by Merrill Lynch & Co., Inc. He also served on the board at Burt's Bees, Inc. and Schering-Plough Corp.



