David H. Komansky

Co-Founder at Fieldpoint Private Bank & Trust, Inc.

                  Fieldpoint Private Bank & Trust, Inc. provides wealth advisory and private banking services. Its services include wealth planning, investment advisory, personal banking and lending, commercial lending, business cash management, and wealth and succession planning. The company was founded in April 2008 and is headquartered in Greenwich, CT.                





